archfeed is a CLI news fetcher for Arch Linux

Usage: archfeed [OPTIONS]

-b --brief
  do not  print news

-d --display [INTEGER]
  specify number of entries to display (newest first)
    use 0 to display all entries (default)
    use -b if you do not want to display any entries

-f --file [FILE]
  specify download location
    default location is ./news

-l --local
  do not download news (use local copy)

-o --online
  download news (default)

-v --verbose
  print news (default)

-h --help
  display this message and exit
